过了。海樱说，爱与遗憾总是交错存在。爷爷留下的各种各样生活的痕迹，在 8 年后，又重新传达给他最疼爱的孙女。这让海樱感觉，爷爷似乎从没离开过，他一直陪在自己身边。女孩在旧日历中发现去世爷爷日记，遗憾没多陪伴 _ 海樱 _ 生日 _ 时候"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-dcbb92818f931e152375cbc06c77615d_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "70 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/593965233"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IpYqFwfyHzdwvEAMaCDk0MjczNzE3IPP6uKEGMAA4IUAQcgk1OTM5NjUyMzN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1680836657.1000984", "card_id": "Q_593961742", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 119}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "过程重要，还是结果重要?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-1940a0b5b57103898c96ce168ac5ce41_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "68 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/593961742"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IpYqFwfyHzdwvEAMaCDk0MjcyOTM1INXtuKEGMAE4jQFAEXIJNTkzOTYxNzQyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1680836657.1007261", "card_id": "Q_591071276", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 211}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "单身上班族，有哪些厨房小家电推荐？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我是一个上班族，经常一个人在家做饭吃，想买一些适合自己使用的厨房小家电，比如电饭锅或者电烤箱之类的，不知道有什么好的推荐？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-14dd4491a4c7241acef75730ae649896_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "63 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/591071276"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IpYqFwfyHzdwvEAMaCDkzNjMwODI4IODj5qAGMAA4hAJAEnIJNTkxMDcxMjc2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA